---
title: Chutney Chicken Curry with rice and green beans
description: This delicious chicken curry can be categorised as having an array of different textures and tastes.  Green beans add vibrancy and good-for-you nutrients while the curry powder, chutney and creme fraiche combine to make a creamy, sweet and slightly spiced sauce which works wonderfully with the tender chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R06_W11_IE_IEXCFC21697-3_Main_high-fe798aa1.jpg
